message: Are you planning a particular woodworking project this summer?

Frustrating weather and family travel have added good excuses to my Making endeavors, but one of my summer ambitions is to get into a wood working project.  I was reminded of that today when I saw this great patio table for board games.  http://boardgamegeek.com/geeklist/66740/making-a-game-table-for-the-patio
Trying to decide on plans for a boring old breadbox :)
I'm making a set of Adirondack chairs and an massive hutch for my kitchen. A good source for plans is http://www.plansnow.com/. I use Google SketchUp for my own designs.
